Set up symbolic links like so:
./vimrc                 -> ~/.vimrc
./ftdetect/notes.vim    -> ~/.vim/ftdetect/notes.vim
./colors/orclord.vim    -> ~/.vim/colors/orclord.vim
./syntax/note.vim       -> ~/.vim/syntax/note.vim

The "bclose" plugin for simplifying buffer management care of
http://vim.wikia.com/wiki/Deleting_a_buffer_without_closing_the_window
